{"tid":2356246,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"700磅重韓Rapper手術途中離世 終年42歲","createTime":"2021-01-06T16:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T18:10:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a35649ae1173815f1f0e6742e4821f487c3c82c","tid":2356246,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e-kamFyW4Ny38DS9EJO3HtLAzvM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MI2C577FZ5FFTCQRUWLR6PD2NU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe-kamFyW4Ny38DS9EJO3HtLAzvM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMI2C577FZ5FFTCQRUWLR6PD2NU.jpg&h=2cff001d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國Rapper Big Joe今日離世，終年42歲。<br />\n<br />\n現年42歲的韓國男Rapper Big Joe，上月底被爆因心功能衰竭、糖尿病而入院接受治療，更要在頸上開個小洞、連接管道來呼吸。不過根據韓媒報道Big Joe因健康惡化，在醫院進行了手術，但於手術途中因流血不止而死亡，今日於京畿道金浦市的一家醫院離世，終年42歲。<br />\n<br />\nHip Hop組合出道<br />\nBig Joe於2008年以Hip Hop組合Holla Dang的一員出道，當時憑身高186cm、體重550磅的巨大身形而受到關注。雖然Big Joe曾一度減肥至330磅，但體重卻反彈至704磅，令健康越來越差，連行路都成問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gJ-9oxhhpf_JC_ef9MVGi4JcZUY=/802x455/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XLOP2SWICRA6XLXEAKXQ7DZWTA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgJ-9oxhhpf_JC_ef9MVGi4JcZUY%3D%2F802x455%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXLOP2SWICRA6XLXEAKXQ7DZWTA.jpeg&h=a4710d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r4nhQR4WHK4NRpIeC7iQIZ14T14=/802x442/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6FMD5FNZBVDINLFFMQ4PTNPISU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresiz